### Health
GET http://localhost:4000/health

### List products
GET http://localhost:4000/api/products

### Create cart
# @name createCart
POST http://localhost:4000/api/carts
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Add item to cart (replace IDs)
PUT http://localhost:4000/api/carts/{{createCart.response.body.cartId}}/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "REPLACE_WITH_PRODUCT_UUID",
  "quantity": 2
}

### Get cold chain summary
GET http://localhost:4000/api/meat/cold-chain/{{createCart.response.body.cartId}}

### Create order
# @name createOrder
POST http://localhost:4000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
